---
// Privacy Notice page. UK GDPR/PECR-aware. DRAFT — NOT yet go-live ready.
// Before real traffic, the business owner must fill every "[to confirm: ...]"
// placeholder (registered/trading name + legal status, business postal address,
// ICO registration number, retention period, the "last updated" date), the
// international-transfer wording should be checked against each provider, and
// the whole notice reviewed by a data-protection professional before any
// marketing capability is added (Phase 4 / PECR). See ROADMAP.md and docs/DESIGN.md §11.
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Notice | Intelligent Carpet Cleaning"
  description="How Intelligent Carpet Cleaning collects, uses, and protects your personal information when you use the site, chat with our AI assistant, or book a clean."
>
  <header class="page-hero">
    <h1>Privacy Notice</h1>
    <p>How Intelligent Carpet Cleaning collects, uses, and protects your personal information.</p>
  </header>

  <div class="legal-wrap">
    <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: [to confirm: date]. This notice explains what we do with your personal data when you use this website, chat with our AI assistant, or book a clean.</p>

    <h2>Who we are</h2>
    <p>This website is operated by Intelligent Carpet Cleaning ([to confirm: registered trading name and legal status, for example sole trader, or limited company name and number]), based in Cheltenham, Gloucestershire. We are the data controller for the personal information described in this notice.</p>
    <p>You can contact us about your data by email at <a href="mailto:talktoregency@gmail.com">talktoregency@gmail.com</a>, by phone on 01242 279590, or by post at [to confirm: business postal address]. Our ICO registration number is [to confirm: ICO registration number].</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>Depending on how you use the site, we may collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Your name, phone number, and email address.</li>
      <li>The address and postcode where the work is to be carried out.</li>
      <li>Details you give us about your property, carpets, and any concerns or staining, including any photographs you choose to upload.</li>
      <li>The content of your conversation with our AI assistant.</li>
      <li>Limited technical data such as your IP address, which we use to keep the service secure and prevent abuse.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How we use it, and our lawful basis</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To answer your enquiry and prepare a quote, on the basis of our legitimate interest in responding to you and to take steps at your request before entering a contract.</li>
      <li>To arrange, confirm, and carry out your booking, to perform our contract with you.</li>
      <li>To send you a booking confirmation by email, to perform our contract with you.</li>
      <li>To protect the website from abuse and overuse (including limiting requests by IP address), on the basis of our legitimate interest in keeping the service available and secure.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>We do not use your details for marketing without your clear consent, and you can withdraw that consent at any time.</p>

    <h2>Our AI assistant</h2>
    <p>Your enquiry is handled by an AI assistant, and any photographs you upload are analysed by AI to help identify your carpet type and recommend a cleaning method. No decision with a legal or similarly significant effect is made about you by automated means alone. Mark personally reviews and confirms every booking.</p>

    <h2>Who we share it with</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal data. We share it only with the service providers that allow us to run the service, who act on our instructions:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Anthropic, which provides the AI assistant that processes your messages and any uploaded photos.</li>
      <li>Resend, which sends your booking confirmation email.</li>
      <li>Netlify, which hosts this website and stores booking records.</li>
      <li>Google, where we generate a calendar link so we can add your appointment to our diary.</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Some of these providers may process data outside the UK. Where they do, we rely on appropriate safeguards such as UK or EU approved transfer mechanisms. [to confirm: review the transfer position with each provider before go-live.]</p>

    <h2>How long we keep it</h2>
    <p>We keep booking records for as long as we need them to provide the service and to meet our legal and accounting obligations (typically [to confirm: 6] years for financial records), after which we delete them. Enquiry conversations that do not lead to a booking are kept only for a short period.</p>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>This site does not use advertising or tracking cookies. The information you enter in the chat stays in your browser for the duration of your visit and is only sent to us when you submit a booking.</p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to ask us for a copy of your data, to correct it, to delete it, to restrict or object to how we use it, and to receive it in a portable format. To exercise any of these, email <a href="mailto:talktoregency@gmail.com">talktoregency@gmail.com</a> and we will respond within one month.</p>

    <h2>Complaints</h2>
    <p>If you have a concern about how we handle your data, please contact us first so we can put it right. You also have the right to complain to the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) at <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ico.org.uk</a> or by calling 0303 123 1113.</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-hero{margin-top:70px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--navy-dark) 0%,var(--navy) 100%);padding:3rem 2rem;text-align:center;}
  .page-hero h1{font-family:"Raleway",sans-serif;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:800;color:#fff;margin-bottom:0.5rem;}
  .page-hero p{color:rgba(255,255,255,0.7);font-size:1rem;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto;}
  .legal-wrap{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:2.5rem 1.5rem;color:var(--text-mid);line-height:1.7;font-size:0.95rem;}
  .legal-meta{color:var(--text-light);font-size:0.85rem;margin-bottom:2rem;}
  .legal-wrap h2{font-family:"Raleway",sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;color:var(--navy);margin:1.8rem 0 0.6rem;}
  .legal-wrap p{margin-bottom:0.8rem;}
  .legal-wrap ul{margin:0.5rem 0 1rem;padding-left:1.3rem;}
  .legal-wrap li{margin-bottom:0.3rem;}
  .legal-wrap a{color:var(--teal);text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;}
  .legal-wrap a:hover{text-decoration:underline;}
</style>
